claim.claim-text:
1. A multipath all optical regenerator and reshaper, comprising: 
N semiconductor optical amplifiers (“SOA”s); 
M multi-mode interferometers (“MMI”s); 
a plurality of waveguides interconnecting the SOAs and MMIs, 
a plurality of possible inputs for a dirty optical signal at a first wavelength; 
a plurality of possible inputs for a continuous wavelength signal at a second wavelength; and 
a plurality of possible outputs of for a clean signal at the second wavelength; 
wherein the regenerator and reshaper comprises at least two disjoint configurations, each of which can implement the regeneration and reshaping functionality notwithstanding the failure of one or more SOAs, MMIs or waveguides in the other configurations.
